This Proclamation is subject to the condition that the qualified free patent applicants occupying portions of the aforedescribed parcel of land, if any, may be compensated for the value of their respective portions and existing improvements thereon, as may be determined by the National Housing Authority.

In order to facilitate the early development of the area for relocation and slum development and resettlement program purposes, the National Housing Authority in coordination with the Bureau of Lands, National Steel Corporation and the City of Iligan, is hereby ordered to immediately conduct the necessary subdivision survey of the same into appropriate homelots, roadlots and other lands for public purposes. The National Housing Authority is hereby given the authority to develop and administer the disposition of these lots in accordance with the guidelines of the Slum Improvement and Resettlement Program.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 7th day of December, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and eighty-one.

(Sgd.) FERDINAND E. MARCOS President of the Philippines

By the President: (Sgd.) JUAN C. TUVERA Presidential Executive Assistant

